		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Are you sure it's an NES on a chip, not a Colecovision on a chip? I'd imagine that because the Colecovision, the MSX1, and an early Sega console used pretty much the same chipset, this chipset might be ASIC'd too.

		

		</td>
